Bank of America Cuts Jobs, to Close 10% of Branches, WSJ Says

-- B y   C h r i s   P e t e r s o n
-- 
2011-03-15T06:11:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-15/bank-of-america-cuts-jobs-to-close-10-of-branches-wsj-says.html
  Bank of America Corp. (BAC)  cut 100 jobs
from its consumer and small-business banking unit and intends to
close 10 percent of its branches over the next few years, the
 Wall Street Journal  reported, citing an unidentified
spokeswoman.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chris Peterson in London at 
 cpeterson@bloomberg.net  